metadata.name: Lifetime Member #1
metadata.title: DCG Mastermind Membership
metadata.description: 50 unique NFT's that gives you lifetime access to Membership in the DCG mastermind. The owner of this NFT is granted a license to be recognized as an official DCG represented in the physical world and the metaverse. The Lifetime NFT is a unique nft representing the DCG physical office location.   The Lifetime NFT owner will be recorded in a master index directory updated twice a year with the approved DCG location for members to locate. The DCG Lifetime NFT gives the owner access to have a Certified DCG location and access to the Mastermind Chat. You may create a DCG LLC with this Lifetime NFT Number.
